{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/shortpromo.gif?t=1734733968\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/advbeg.png?t=1734733968\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro-style <strong>FANTASY BEAT'EM'UP / HACK'N'SLASH</strong>, inspired by classic cult games of 90s! Blood, loot, skills - what's not to love?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gold edition is created to rethink and refine some of the gameplay features and balance of the original game and to add some asked features! And also - well, let's be honest here - to raise some financial support for the Chapter 2 development! So if you're waiting for C2 - please consider supporting us by getting the Gold edition! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/testFeaturesv3.png?t=1734733968\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play alone or with a friend and, as mighty <strong>WARRIOR</strong>, agile <strong>ACROBAT </strong>or powerful <strong>MAGUS</strong>, master the art of fighting. Game features three levels of difficulty - for new players, veterans and seasoned hardcore players. Fully original soundtrack and voiced dialogues will help you to immerse yourself into the mysterious world of Ijmeria and defend your people against brutal invaders! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/alltogether2.png?t=1734733968\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/features.png?t=1734733968\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">unique <strong>FANTASY</strong> setting - no elves and dwarfs here, promise!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>skill-based</strong> combat with <strong>special moves, throws, blocks and ripostes</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">army of enemies with <strong>unique behavior</strong> and combat moves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">hours long story-driven adventure, featuring <strong>NPCs and quests</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">fully voiced dialogues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">open map to explore and choose your path</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>loot system</strong> - weapons, armor, potions and items to find, equip and use</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>RPG system</strong> - combat moves, skills and perks to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">original soundtrack</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734733968","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/page.bg.jpg?t=1734733968","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/271938618e0e62c1eabbd21065335d71eb5ba4f4/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734733968","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/271938618e0e62c1eabbd21065335d71eb5ba4f4/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734733968","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play on TV","id":43},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"A bit of cartoonish violence - pixel swords hit pixel bodies, pixel blood, p